*Razgovarali* su dugo, pa i na teme koje ih nisu zanimali. (They talked for a long time, even about topics that didn't interest them.)

Oni su *razgovarali* o svim važnim stvarima. (They talked about all the important matters.)

*Razgovarala* je sa njim o njegovom poslu. (She talked to him about his job.)

Oni su *razgovarali* o njenom novom projektu. (They talked about her new project.)

Nisu *razgovarali* o tome još dugo. (They didn't talk about it for long.)